Title: Jau Tithe Khau
Actors: Makarand Anaspure, Kuldip Pawar, Dipali Sayyad, Chetan Dalvi
Plot: Jau Tithe Khau is a Marathi movie that released in 2007. Produced by Meghraj Rajebhosle & directed by Abhay Kirti. The movie is based on the protagonist who is fed up of corruption everywhere and decides to teach everyone a lesson.
